properties.Description:
ECOA is a code representing the ownership designation on the account.

B On Behalf of Another
C Co-Applicant / Co-Maker
I Individual
J Joint
M Maker
S Shared
T Terminated
U Undesignated
W Work Related
Z Authorized User
